  "body": "Hi everyone\r\n\r\n#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: 1.9.9\r\nOS & Version:Ubuntu Linux 18.04\r\nCommit hash : (if `develop`)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nDefine lower that one the GasFloor and GasPrice\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nit is limited to 1. not let use 0.00001\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\nIf I set \"0.0001\"as Gasprice, Geth drop an error of integral number, then it cannot use it. \r\n\r\nif I set -1, transaction pool price threshold will update to \"1000000000\". \r\n\r\n#####why lower ..\r\n1) I am looking for the block reward, as I am solo miner, I will accept lower fee.\r\n3) Pools are behaving as a banks. as they have all the power for process the transactions. if you open an opportunity to every solo miner, it will change the game rules.\r\n2)Lower fees makes a reason why use ethereum instead of a current bank transaction\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
